{
  "suite_version": 1,
  "date": "2026-07-22",
  "description": "Leg D agent-accuracy task suite. Each task is a natural-language request plus machine-checkable ground truth. Classes: well_posed (generate cleanly), fixable (proceed only with a specific correction or flagged warning), ill_posed (refuse, stating the physics reason). Scoring is deterministic via score_agent_run.py; no LLM judges.",
